text: haey a l laoh ban leukayk borsa pir neak mk thveuchea uteahar del mneak nei ke teangpir noh chea mnoussa k del kmean samotthaphap avei saoh haey ke kuchea bantouk da thngonthngor champoh anapyabal robsa ke . tohchea ke( anapyabal) brae aoy ke tow tinea kadaoy ku ke min del noam mokvinh nouv brakear la laey . tae mean pheap smaekna der ryyte rveang ke( mnoussa k) haeyning anak del brae aoy ke br pru td ampeu you tde thmr haey ke khluoneng sthet leu meakra troemotrauv noh
